209    protected function transformResolverToDocumentation(EnhancedOptionsResolver $resolver): array
210    {
211        $documentationBlock = [];
212        $blockProperties = $this->propertiesThief($resolver);

219                    'allowedTypes' => array_key_exists($name, $blockProperties['allowedTypes']) ? $blockProperties['allowedTypes'][$name] : [],
220                    'allowedValues' => array_key_exists($name, $blockProperties['allowedValues']) ? $blockProperties['allowedValues'][$name] : [],
221                    'extraInformation' => $resolver->getExtraInformation($name),
222                ];
223            }
224        } else {

226        }
227

231    protected function propertiesThief(EnhancedOptionsResolver $resolver): array
232    {
233        $classCastAsArray = (array) $resolver;
234        $propertiesNeeded = [
